thread.title_full: Guardian Self Storage reviewed by Customer

author: Customer
title: Customer
text:
Initial unit not where it was thought to be located but I had little time to return to office until after the weekend. Very happy with resolution. No hassles, quickly changed to more preferable unit. Service excellent.
Only wish door had rope to pull it down because it flew up with little effort, beyond my reach. Fortunate to have a cane to grab the lip.
